         <div type="translation" xml:space="preserve"><head>Translation</head><p><supplied reason="lost">May he be well off</supplied>. Helladios lived approximately 50 years, three months and fifteen days. Christ be with your spirit. He died on the seventh of the month of Payn among the Africans.</p></div>
